{
  "id": "6287b1b0a776ed00223825aa",
  "title": "Scrapboxにブロック引用がない",
  "created": 1653060022,
  "updated": 1655192000,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6287b1b0a776ed00223825aa",
      "text": "Scrapboxにブロック引用がない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653060022,
      "updated": 1653060029
    },
    {
      "id": "6287b1beaff09e00009d87cb",
      "text": "箇条書きされているブロックを手軽にまともなみばえで[引用]できない[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1653060030,
      "updated": 1653168209
    },
    {
      "id": "6287b21faff09e00009d87cf",
      "text": "　箇条書きにタブとスペースが混在することもみばえが悪くなる原因の一つ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653060128,
      "updated": 1653060154
    },
    {
      "id": "6287b20aaff09e00009d87cd",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/032b27b5f4523c7363b5e520557f63d5]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653060106,
      "updated": 1653060115
    },
    {
      "id": "6287b212aff09e00009d87ce",
      "text": " 一度だけ引用内にもbulletが表示されるようになったことがある[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1653060115,
      "updated": 1653168252
    },
    {
      "id": "6289587c1280f000001fdc8f",
      "text": "  この話題以前にも書いたことあるぞ",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1653168252,
      "updated": 1653168267
    },
    {
      "id": "628958621280f000001fdc8d",
      "text": "  つなげたい",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1653168227,
      "updated": 1653168273
    },
    {
      "id": "6289c00ae5172d0000327ad8",
      "text": "  [Scrapboxの引用記法中で箇条書き]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1653194762,
      "updated": 1653194762
    },
    {
      "id": "6289c6481280f000007b0860",
      "text": "  わーいつながった！",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1653196360,
      "updated": 1653196368
    },
    {
      "id": "628958621280f000001fdc8e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1653168227,
      "updated": 1653168227
    },
    {
      "id": "62881ef779d3a90000773e7c",
      "text": "こうなってほしい[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653087992,
      "updated": 1653087994
    },
    {
      "id": "6287b1edaff09e00009d87cc",
      "text": "[/villagepump/「観測範囲が狭い」は侮辱する言葉か？#62865c0a7838e30000be24b8]を例にすると",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653060078,
      "updated": 1653088149
    },
    {
      "id": "62881efb79d3a90000773e7d",
      "text": "\t> 新しい例え話は沢山生まれていますが、話している内容は変わっていないと思う",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653087995,
      "updated": 1653088011
    },
    {
      "id": "62881efb79d3a90000773e7e",
      "text": "\t\t>[nishio.icon]は本筋も進めたいが、その新しい例え話も欲しくて議論を進めている節がある[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653087995,
      "updated": 1653088019
    },
    {
      "id": "62881efb79d3a90000773e7f",
      "text": "\t\t\t>通常の議論と進め方が異なるので相手/ギャラリーが混乱する気がすると感じている[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653087995,
      "updated": 1653088026
    },
    {
      "id": "62881efb79d3a90000773e80",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t>[増井俊之.icon]が気になっていないならいいけど",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653087995,
      "updated": 1653088029
    },
    {
      "id": "62881efb79d3a90000773e81",
      "text": "\t\t\t>チャットと違ってScrapboxは枝が並列的に育つし、どの枝から育てるかをコントロールできないので、……伸びるに任せてから剪定……すればいいと思っている[nishio.icon][Mijinko_SD.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653087995,
      "updated": 1653088186
    },
    {
      "id": "62881efb79d3a90000773e82",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t>新しい議論の形だ！[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653087995,
      "updated": 1653088048
    },
    {
      "id": "62881efb79d3a90000773e83",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t>この感覚はあって、チャットではやらない茶々ととられる思ったことをセーブせずに書いてる[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653087995,
      "updated": 1653088054
    },
    {
      "id": "62881f5479d3a90000773e87",
      "text": " このくらいならscriptで解決しそう[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1653088085,
      "updated": 1653168300
    },
    {
      "id": "628959151280f000001fdc9c",
      "text": "  できた",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1653168405,
      "updated": 1653168421
    },
    {
      "id": "628958a31280f000001fdc92",
      "text": "  code:js",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1653168292,
      "updated": 1653168304
    },
    {
      "id": "628958af1280f000001fdc93",
      "text": "   scrapbox.PopupMenu.addButton({",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1653168304,
      "updated": 1653168312
    },
    {
      "id": "628958b81280f000001fdc94",
      "text": "     title: (text) => text.includes(\"\\n\") ? \">\" : \"\",",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1653168312,
      "updated": 1653168345
    },
    {
      "id": "628958c11280f000001fdc96",
      "text": "     onClick: (text) => text.split(\"\\n\")",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1653168321,
      "updated": 1653168360
    },
    {
      "id": "628958eb1280f000001fdc99",
      "text": "       .map((line) => line.replace(/^(\\s*)/, \"$1>\"))",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1653168363,
      "updated": 1653168387
    },
    {
      "id": "628959061280f000001fdc9a",
      "text": "       .join(\"\\n\"),",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1653168390,
      "updated": 1653168399
    },
    {
      "id": "628958b91280f000001fdc95",
      "text": "   });",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1653168313,
      "updated": 1653168402
    },
    {
      "id": "628959111280f000001fdc9b",
      "text": "   ",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1653168402,
      "updated": 1653168402
    },
    {
      "id": "628958941280f000001fdc90",
      "text": "\t\t👍[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653168277,
      "updated": 1653168510
    },
    {
      "id": "6289597b79d3a90000b6a8ce",
      "text": "\tが、見た感じなんか汚い？慣れない？し、ベストな解が他にある気はするなぁ……[sta.icon][Mijinko_SD.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1653168509,
      "updated": 1653204256
    },
    {
      "id": "62895e9979d3a90000a5bdab",
      "text": "\t\t引用はコードと同じくブロック的（インデントの深さが揃っている）な方が自然に思える",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653169819,
      "updated": 1653169901
    },
    {
      "id": "628961df79d3a90000a5bdae",
      "text": "\t\tトレードオフなのかしら",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653170657,
      "updated": 1653170664
    },
    {
      "id": "62a834ff385a920000d662ec",
      "text": "一時期だけこの方法でデプロイされてたけど、なんか不具合があってrevertされたような気がする[miyamonz.icon]",
      "userId": "5953adab7aa58a0011385a92",
      "created": 1655190784,
      "updated": 1655190784
    },
    {
      "id": "62a839aa1280f00000d28d1b",
      "text": " [Scrapboxの引用記法中で箇条書き]ですね[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1655191978,
      "updated": 1655192000
    },
    {
      "id": "62a834ff385a920000d662ed",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5953adab7aa58a0011385a92",
      "created": 1655190784,
      "updated": 1655190784
    },
    {
      "id": "62a834ff385a920000d662eb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5953adab7aa58a0011385a92",
      "created": 1655190783,
      "updated": 1655190783
    },
    {
      "id": "62a74e60e5172d00008e977a",
      "text": "[Copy Plain (Scrapbox)]して引用記法内にぶちこむという手もある[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1655131746,
      "updated": 1655131771
    },
    {
      "id": "62a74e7be5172d00008e977c",
      "text": "　bullet（Scrapboxのではなく`・`）がつく",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1655131773,
      "updated": 1655131826
    },
    {
      "id": "62a74eb3e5172d00008e977d",
      "text": "　ただしリンクが外れ、アイコンが`(名前)`になる",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1655131829,
      "updated": 1655131858
    },
    {
      "id": "62a74e61e5172d00008e977b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1655131746,
      "updated": 1655131746
    },
    {
      "id": "6289620079d3a90000a5bdb0",
      "text": "ここまででてきた方法",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653170691,
      "updated": 1653170697
    },
    {
      "id": "6289622179d3a90000a5bdb3",
      "text": "\t1: インデントなしの引用記法内にぶちこむ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653170722,
      "updated": 1653170842
    },
    {
      "id": "6289627479d3a90000a5bdb7",
      "text": "\t\tby [nishio.icon]、[Scrapboxにブロック引用がない#6287b21faff09e00009d87cf]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653170806,
      "updated": 1655131899
    },
    {
      "id": "62a74efbaff09e00004d6564",
      "text": "\t\t　全く良い方法だと思ってない「こんな挙動になっておかしい」の意味で出したもの[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1655131899,
      "updated": 1655131918
    },
    {
      "id": "6289628679d3a90000a5bdb8",
      "text": " 2: 1に加えてbulletもつける",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653170823,
      "updated": 1653170825
    },
    {
      "id": "6289c01de5172d0000327ad9",
      "text": "  [Scrapboxの引用記法中で箇条書き]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1653194781,
      "updated": 1653196888
    },
    {
      "id": "628961ff79d3a90000a5bdaf",
      "text": "\t3: コピペした行ごとにインデントを守りつつ`>`をつける",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653170688,
      "updated": 1653170773
    },
    {
      "id": "6289625879d3a90000a5bdb6",
      "text": "\t\tby [sta.icon]、[Scrapboxにブロック引用がない#62881f5479d3a90000773e87]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1653170778,
      "updated": 1653170832
    },
    {
      "id": "6289623179d3a90000a5bdb5",
      "text": " 4: ブロックを引用する記法はない、と諦めて引用記法を使わない[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1653170739,
      "updated": 1655131959
    },
    {
      "id": "62a74f12aff09e00004d6565",
      "text": "\t\tこれいいかも[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1655131922,
      "updated": 1655160681
    },
